msgid "Caching — saves API credits"
msgstr "Caching — spart API-Guthaben"

#: admin/class-admin-settings.php:5350
msgid "Caching reuses the result of past IP lookups instead of asking the community network again. Typically saves 70–90% of API calls."
msgstr "Caching verwendet das Ergebnis vergangener IP-Abfragen erneut, anstatt das Community-Netzwerk erneut zu fragen. Spart typischerweise 70–90 % der API-Aufrufe."

